# The committed official campaigns file is a DEV-ONLY seed fixture (the weekly bake). It is
# deliberately kept OUT of the prod image so stale/test data is physically impossible to serve — the
# live DB is the single source of truth in production (backend/server.js officialWorkspace, and the
# client's loadOfficialCampaigns gates its fixture fallback on import.meta.env.DEV). Excluded from the
# build context ⇒ vite never copies it into dist ⇒ it isn't in the running container.
